# Placeholder — K8s secrets should never be committed to version control.
# 
# For local development, use:
#   kubectl apply -f k8s/secrets/app-secrets.yaml
#
# For production, use Sealed Secrets:
#   https://github.com/bitnami-labs/sealed-secrets
#
# Or External Secrets Operator (ESO) with a secrets backend
# such as HashiCorp Vault or AWS Secrets Manager.
